2. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking): The paper deals with channel observations and decoding metrics, which are key components in communication and networking systems. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an unsupervised learning approach based on expectation maximization, which is a machine learning technique.
